INSTALL OPENCV di Python3 (sistem operasi linux, distro xubuntu 18.04 64 bit)
1. Install package virtualenv
    sudo apt-get install virtualenv (done)
2. install package tkinter python3
    sudo apt-get install python3-tk (done)
3. Buat virtual environtment yang bernama "cvenv"
    virtualenv -p python3 cvenv (done)
4. mengaktifkan virtualenv cvenv
    source cvenv/bin/activate (done) -> muncul (cvenv)
5. Check isi library di virtualenv cvenv
    pip list (aman)
6. install opencv
    pip install opencv-python (done)
7. check opencv 
    buka python
    import cv2 (done)
8. check isi library terbaru
    ada opencv-python :)

Terimakasih
Aglissae
